Welche Farbe erhält der Absatz <code>&lt;p id="info" class="notice"&gt;Hinweis&lt;/p&gt;</code>?<br><div class="code-card" style="max-width:900px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:#102d42;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.16);font-family:Consolas,'Courier New',monospace;margin:12px 0;"><div style="height:42px;background:#12334a;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 16px;color:#fff;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-weight:700;"><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ff5f57;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ffbd2e;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#28c840;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:13px;"></span>style.css</div><pre style="margin:0;padding:18px 20px;color:#f8fbff;line-height:1.48;font-size:15px;white-space:pre-wrap;background:#102d42;">p { color: gray; }
.notice { color: orange; }
#info { color: navy; }</pre></div>

Welche Aussage beschreibt das Layout korrekt?<br><div class="code-card" style="max-width:900px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:#102d42;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.16);font-family:Consolas,'Courier New',monospace;margin:12px 0;"><div style="height:42px;background:#12334a;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 16px;color:#fff;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-weight:700;"><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ff5f57;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ffbd2e;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#28c840;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:13px;"></span>style.css</div><pre style="margin:0;padding:18px 20px;color:#f8fbff;line-height:1.48;font-size:15px;white-space:pre-wrap;background:#102d42;">.nav {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}</pre></div>

Wie wirkt <code>justify-content: center</code> in diesem Beispiel?<br><div class="code-card" style="max-width:900px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:#102d42;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.16);font-family:Consolas,'Courier New',monospace;margin:12px 0;"><div style="height:42px;background:#12334a;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 16px;color:#fff;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-weight:700;"><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ff5f57;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ffbd2e;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#28c840;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:13px;"></span>style.css</div><pre style="margin:0;padding:18px 20px;color:#f8fbff;line-height:1.48;font-size:15px;white-space:pre-wrap;background:#102d42;">.panel {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
}</pre></div>

Welche Aussage passt zu diesem Grid?<br><div class="code-card" style="max-width:900px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:#102d42;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.16);font-family:Consolas,'Courier New',monospace;margin:12px 0;"><div style="height:42px;background:#12334a;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 16px;color:#fff;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-weight:700;"><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ff5f57;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ffbd2e;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#28c840;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:13px;"></span>style.css</div><pre style="margin:0;padding:18px 20px;color:#f8fbff;line-height:1.48;font-size:15px;white-space:pre-wrap;background:#102d42;">.layout {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr;
}</pre></div>

Welche Aussage beschreibt den Code korrekt?<br><div class="code-card" style="max-width:900px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:#102d42;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.16);font-family:Consolas,'Courier New',monospace;margin:12px 0;"><div style="height:42px;background:#12334a;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 16px;color:#fff;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-weight:700;"><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ff5f57;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ffbd2e;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#28c840;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:13px;"></span>style.css</div><pre style="margin:0;padding:18px 20px;color:#f8fbff;line-height:1.48;font-size:15px;white-space:pre-wrap;background:#102d42;">.cards {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
  gap: 1rem;
}</pre></div>

Wie wird das Layout bei einer Viewportbreite von 500px dargestellt?<br><div class="code-card" style="max-width:900px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:#102d42;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.16);font-family:Consolas,'Courier New',monospace;margin:12px 0;"><div style="height:42px;background:#12334a;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 16px;color:#fff;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-weight:700;"><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ff5f57;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ffbd2e;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#28c840;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:13px;"></span>style.css</div><pre style="margin:0;padding:18px 20px;color:#f8fbff;line-height:1.48;font-size:15px;white-space:pre-wrap;background:#102d42;">.layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
@media (max-width: 650px) {
  .layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}</pre></div>

Welche Refactoring-Lösung ist für diesen Code am sinnvollsten?<br><div class="code-card" style="max-width:900px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:#102d42;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.16);font-family:Consolas,'Courier New',monospace;margin:12px 0;"><div style="height:42px;background:#12334a;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 16px;color:#fff;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-weight:700;"><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ff5f57;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ffbd2e;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#28c840;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:13px;"></span>style.css</div><pre style="margin:0;padding:18px 20px;color:#f8fbff;line-height:1.48;font-size:15px;white-space:pre-wrap;background:#102d42;">.header { color: #003964; }
.card-title { color: #003964; }
.footer-title { color: #003964; }</pre></div>
